'''斯特凡纳·德內夫'''（{{lang-fr|Stéphane Denève}}，{{bd|1971年|11月24日||}}），法國[[指揮家|指揮家]]。現任{{Link-en|布鲁塞尔爱乐乐团|Brussels Philharmonic}}及[[聖路易交響樂團|聖路易交響樂團]]音樂總監。

== 生平 ==
德内夫生于法国[[图尔宽|图尔宽]]，<ref>Tim Cornwell, "Swing time for Stéphane". ''The Scotsman'', 1 October 2005.</ref>毕业于[[巴黎音乐学院|巴黎音乐学院]]。曾先后在[[巴黎管弦乐团|巴黎管弦乐团]]担任[[乔治·索尔蒂|乔治·索尔蒂]]的助理指挥，在[[國立巴黎歌劇團|国立巴黎歌剧团]]担任[[乔治·普雷特|乔治·普雷特]]的助理指挥，在1998年{{Le|小泽征尔松本音乐节|Seiji Ozawa Matsumoto Festival}}担任[[小泽征尔|小泽征尔]]的助理指挥。

2005年9月起，德内夫担任{{Le|皇家苏格兰国家管弦乐团|Royal Scottish National Orchestra}}（RSNO）的音乐总监，他带领乐团参加了2006年的[[逍遥音乐会|逍遥音乐会]]，并进行了乐团在法国的首次演出。<ref>{{cite web|title=Avant garde alliance|url=http://scotlandonsunday.scotsman.com/review.cfm?id=257002006|access-date=2007-05-21|author=Sarah Jones|date=2006-02-19|work=Scotland on Sunday|archive-url=https://archive.today/20120527051652/http://scotlandonsunday.scotsman.com/review.cfm?id=257002006|archive-date=2012-05-27|url-status=dead}}</ref>两次延长任期后，德内夫于2011-2012乐季结束时解任RSNO的音乐总监职务。<ref>{{cite press release|url=http://www.rsno.org.uk/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=549:stephane-deneve-joins-stuttgart-radio-symphony-orchestra-swr-from-2011-and-extends-rsno-contract-to-end-of-2011-12-season-&catid=41:press-releases&Itemid=147|title=RSNO Music Director commits through 2012 and announces new European appointment|publisher=Royal Scottish National Orchestra|date=March 2010|accessdate=2010-03-06|archive-date=2011-07-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110726152759/http://www.rsno.org.uk/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=549:stephane-deneve-joins-stuttgart-radio-symphony-orchestra-swr-from-2011-and-extends-rsno-contract-to-end-of-2011-12-season-&catid=41:press-releases&Itemid=147}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.heraldscotland.com/news/home-news/national-orchestra-maestro-to-leave-scotland-1.1010874|title=National orchestra maestro to leave Scotland|work=The Herald|author=Phil Miller|date=2010-03-04|accessdate=2010-03-06|archive-date=2011-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110927111854/http://www.heraldscotland.com/news/home-news/national-orchestra-maestro-to-leave-scotland-1.1010874}}</ref>德内夫与RSNO为[[拿索斯唱片|Naxos]]和Chandos唱片公司录制了多张唱片。

2009年10月，代替[[米歇尔·普拉松|米歇尔·普拉松]]，德内夫首次客座指挥了[[斯图加特广播交响乐团|斯图加特广播交响乐团]]。<ref name="Thieme">{{cite news|url=https://www.stuttgarter-zeitung.de/inhalt.chefdirigent-stephane-den-ve-am-pult-des-rso-steht-nun-ein-lockenkopf.95e750fc-925a-4dc1-9628-838be86e48b6.html|title=Am Pult des RSO steht nun ein Lockenkopf|work=Stuttgarter Zeitung|author=Götz Thieme|date=2011-09-22|accessdate=2012-01-08|archive-date=2020-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201203174846/https://www.stuttgarter-zeitung.de/inhalt.chefdirigent-stephane-den-ve-am-pult-des-rso-steht-nun-ein-lockenkopf.95e750fc-925a-4dc1-9628-838be86e48b6.html}}</ref>以这次合作为基础，次年3月，乐团宣布了德内夫成为其第六任首席指挥的任命，自2011–2012乐季生效 ，<ref>{{cite press release|url=http://www.swr.de/orchester-und-ensembles/orchester/stephane-deneve-jahrespressekonferenz/-/id=788382/did=6074478/nid=788382/3myy4j/index.html|title=Radio-Sinfonieorchester Stuttgart: Neuer Chefdirigent – Stéphane Denève ist ab September 2011 Chefdirigent beim RSO Stuttgart|publisher=Stuttgart Radio Symphony Orchestra|date=2010-03-03|accessdate=2015-09-13}}</ref>初始合同期为三年。<ref name="Thieme2">{{cite news|url=https://www.stuttgarter-zeitung.de/inhalt.chefdirigent-stephane-den-ve-am-pult-des-rso-steht-nun-ein-lockenkopf.95e750fc-925a-4dc1-9628-838be86e48b6.html|title=Am Pult des RSO steht nun ein Lockenkopf|work=Stuttgarter Zeitung|author=Götz Thieme|date=2011-09-22|accessdate=2012-01-08|archive-date=2020-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201203174846/https://www.stuttgarter-zeitung.de/inhalt.chefdirigent-stephane-den-ve-am-pult-des-rso-steht-nun-ein-lockenkopf.95e750fc-925a-4dc1-9628-838be86e48b6.html}}</ref>2013年6月宣布延期至2015–2016乐季。<ref>{{cite press release|url=http://www.swr.de/unternehmen/kommunikation/6-dirigent-deneve-bleibt-bis-2016/-/id=10563098/did=11540424/nid=10563098/yr0ysk/index.html|title=Dirigent Denève bleibt bis 2016|publisher=SWR|date=2013-06-06|accessdate=2014-06-28}}{{Dead link|date=February 2019}}</ref>德内夫也成为斯图加特广播交响乐团与[[西南广播电台巴登巴登与弗莱堡交响乐团|西南广播电台巴登巴登与弗莱堡交响乐团]]合并之前的最后一任首席指挥。

2013年11月，德内夫首次客座指挥了{{Le|布鲁塞尔爱乐乐团|Brussels Philharmonic}}。 2014年6月，布鲁塞尔爱乐宣布任命德内夫为下一任音乐总监，从2015-2016乐季开始生效。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://trends.knack.be/economie/bedrijven/brussels-philharmonic-profileert-zich-met-nieuwe-dirigent/article-normal-261381.html|title=Brussels Philharmonic profileert zich met nieuwe dirigent|work=Knack|author=Roeland Byl|date=2014-06-27|accessdate=2014-06-28|archive-date=2021-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210620194242/https://trends.knack.be/economie/bedrijven/brussels-philharmonic-profileert-zich-met-nieuwe-dirigent/article-normal-261381.html}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.gramophone.co.uk/news/st%C3%A9phane-den%C3%A8ve-to-become-chief-conductor-of-the-brussels-philharmonic|title=Stéphane Denève to become Chief Conductor of the Brussels Philharmonic|work=Gramophone|author=James McCarthy|date=2014-06-27|accessdate=2014-06-28|archive-date=2014-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140723085154/http://www.gramophone.co.uk/news/st%C3%A9phane-den%C3%A8ve-to-become-chief-conductor-of-the-brussels-philharmonic}}</ref>德内夫任内的一项新举措是成立了未来管弦乐曲目中心（CffOR），用于委托创作新作品。2017年，德内夫指挥布鲁塞尔爱乐乐团在[[伊丽莎白女王音乐比赛|伊丽莎白女王大赛]]的首届大提琴比赛中演出。 德内夫计划在2021-2022演出季结束时结束他在布鲁塞尔爱乐乐团的音乐总监职位。<ref>{{cite press release|url=https://www.brusselsphilharmonic.be/magazine/kazushi-ono-nieuwe-muziekdirecteur|title=Kazushi Ono nieuwe muziekdirecteur|publisher=Brussels Philharmonic|date=2021-09-29|access-date=2021-10-06|archive-date=2021-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211007025512/https://www.brusselsphilharmonic.be/magazine/kazushi-ono-nieuwe-muziekdirecteur}}</ref>2022年1月，[[荷蘭廣播愛樂樂團|荷兰广播爱乐乐团]]（RFO）宣布任命德内夫为其下一任首席客座指挥，从2023-2024演出季开始。 德内夫曾在2014年客座指挥过RFO。<ref>{{cite press release|url=https://www.radiofilharmonischorkest.nl/nieuws/stephane-deneve-vaste-gastdirigent-van-het-radio-filharmonisch-orkest/|title=Stéphane Denève vaste gastdirigent van het Radio Filharmonisch Orkest|publisher=Radio Filharmonisch Orkest|date=2022-01-13|accessdate=2022-01-14|archive-date=2022-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220116022955/https://www.radiofilharmonischorkest.nl/nieuws/stephane-deneve-vaste-gastdirigent-van-het-radio-filharmonisch-orkest/}}</ref>

1999年，德内夫在{{Le|圣达菲歌剧院|Santa Fe Opera}}指挥[[弗朗西斯·普朗克|普朗克]]的《[[聖衣會修女對話錄|圣衣会修女对话录]]》首次亮相美国。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9A0CE7DC1230F934A3575BC0A96F958260&sec=&spon=&pagewanted=all|title=Music Review: A Striking New Design For Poulenc's Nuns|work=New York Times|author=Anthony Tommasini|date=1999-08-07|accessdate=2007-05-21|archive-date=2008-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081022191249/http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9A0CE7DC1230F934A3575BC0A96F958260&sec=&spon=&pagewanted=all}}</ref>2003年，他首次客座指挥[[聖路易交響樂團|圣路易斯交响乐团]]。 2007年，他首次作为客座指挥出现在[[费城管弦乐团|费城管弦乐团]]。 2014年4月，费城交响乐团任命德内夫为下一任首席客座指挥，从2014-2015乐季生效。<ref>{{cite press release|url=http://www.philorch.org/press-room/news/philadelphia-orchestra-appoints-conducting-roster-principal-guest-conductor|title=The Philadelphia Orchestra Appoints Conducting Roster of Principal Guest Conductor, Conductor-in-Residence, and Assistant Conductor|publisher=The Philadelphia Orchestra|date=2014-04-28|accessdate=2014-06-28|archive-date=2015-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150403021735/https://www.philorch.org/press-room/news/philadelphia-orchestra-appoints-conducting-roster-principal-guest-conductor}}</ref>2017年2月，乐团宣布将德内夫的首席客座指挥合同延长至2019-2020乐季。<ref>{{cite press release|url=https://www.philorch.org/press-room/news/philadelphia-orchestra-extends-st%C3%A9phane-den%C3%A8ve%E2%80%99s-contract-principal-guest-conductor#/|title=The Philadelphia Orchestra Extends Stéphane Denève’s Contract as Principal Guest Conductor for Three More Years, until 2019–20|publisher=The Philadelphia Orchestra|date=2017-02-07|accessdate=2017-02-11|archive-date=2019-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190424041708/https://www.philorch.org/press-room/news/philadelphia-orchestra-extends-st%C3%A9phane-den%C3%A8ve%E2%80%99s-contract-principal-guest-conductor#/}}</ref>2017年6月，圣路易斯交响乐团任命德内夫为下一任音乐总监，从2019-2020乐季生效，初始合同为3个乐季。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/06/07/arts/music/stephane-deneve-next-conductor-of-st-louis-symphony.html|title=A Frenchman Is Named Next Conductor of the St. Louis Symphony|date=2017-06-07|work=The New York Times|access-date=2018-05-18|archive-date=2022-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220316044935/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/06/07/arts/music/stephane-deneve-next-conductor-of-st-louis-symphony.html}}</ref>2021年3月，圣路易斯交响乐团宣布将德内夫的音乐总监合同延长至2025-2026乐季。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.stltoday.com/entertainment/arts-and-theatre/st-louis-symphony-orchestra-extends-dene-ve-s-contract-to-2026/article_85cbe8df-896d-543b-ac65-29f43d60e601.html|title=St. Louis Symphony Orchestra extends Denève’s contract to 2026|work=Saint Louis Post-Dispatch|author=Eric Meyer|date=2021-03-30|accessdate=2021-03-31|archive-date=2022-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220316044930/https://www.stltoday.com/entertainment/arts-and-theatre/st-louis-symphony-orchestra-extends-dene-ve-s-contract-to-2026/article_85cbe8df-896d-543b-ac65-29f43d60e601.html}}</ref>

== 个人生活 ==
2007年7月，德内夫与奥萨·马斯特斯（Åsa Masters）在加利福尼亚结婚，<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.playbillarts.com/news/article/6834.html|title=Love Among the Grapevines: Conductor Weds Between Performances at Napa Valley's Festival del Sole|work=Playbill Arts|author=Matthew Westphal|date=2007-07-24|accessdate=2007-09-07|archive-date=2011-05-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110526203153/http://www.playbillarts.com/news/article/6834.html}}</ref>他们育有有一个女儿阿尔玛<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.heraldscotland.com/arts-ents/music-features/a-modern-day-hero-1.1055139|title=A modern-day hero|work=The Herald|author=Michael Tumelty|date=2010-09-15|accessdate=2010-11-21|archive-date=2012-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121007004520/http://www.heraldscotland.com/arts-ents/music-features/a-modern-day-hero-1.1055139}}</ref>（Alma，2008年出生）。

2008年，德内夫获得了[[赫瑞瓦特大学|赫瑞瓦特大学]]的荣誉文学博士学位。

2020年，德内夫和马斯特斯感染了[[COVID-19|COVID-19]]，随后康复。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.stltoday.com/entertainment/music/st-louis-symphony-orchestra-announces-plans-for-fall/article_b27b6395-f49a-5926-9b2d-229624fbce80.html|title=St. Louis Symphony Orchestra announces plans for fall|work=Saint Louis Post-Dispatch|author=Sarah Bryan Miller|date=2020-08-11|accessdate=2020-11-26|archive-date=2022-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220418050151/https://www.stltoday.com/entertainment/music/st-louis-symphony-orchestra-announces-plans-for-fall/article_b27b6395-f49a-5926-9b2d-229624fbce80.html}}</ref>

